data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER WITH AMAZING OFFERS - LET'S MAKE THIS YOUR NEW HOME!  This fantastic 3 bedroom/2 bath home is not only a gem for Military relocation, first-time homebuyers, families, investment opportunities, or professionals but also an incredible opportunity you won't want to miss! The seller is ready to negotiate and sweeten the deal with some fantastic incentives:   Price Reduction: You'll start with a great price, and now it's even better!   $10,000 in Seller Concessions: That's right, the seller is offering a generous $10,000 towards your closing costs. Imagine the savings!   Preferred Lender Credit: You can also benefit from a 1% credit from the preferred lender, which can go up to $7,500 for a buydown. This means more affordability for you!  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a bright and welcoming atmosphere, flooded with natural light that instantly makes you feel at home. Recent updates, including fresh paint and plush carpet in the bedrooms, have elevated this house's charm to a whole new level.  The spacious living area features laminate wood floors that perfectly complement the inviting fireplace-a cozy sanctuary for relaxation and making lasting memories.  In the kitchen and dining area, you'll find practical and low-maintenance ceramic tiles, making your daily life a breeze. Step outside to a generously sized backyard, a blank canvas ready for your creative landscaping ideas.  Located in the serene northeastern part of San Antonio, this home offers the best of both worlds: peace and easy access to the city. With military bases, hospitals, and an array of shopping and dining options nearby, convenience and comfort go hand in hand.  Don't miss this golden opportunity to make this your forever home! Let's schedule a showing and explore all the exciting possibilities that await you in this fantastic property. Your dream home is just a step away!
